ef="http://wplook.com/accommodate" target="_blank">Accommodate</a> is absolutely the one you are looking for.</p>\n<p>The theme is equipped with an online booking form where visitors can book and share a room, read your latest tweets, see the hotel location on the map and take a look at the beautiful FancyBox gallery.<span id="more-1634"></span></p>\n<div id="attachment_1635" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 535px"><a href="http://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Accommodate-WordPress-Theme.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-1635" title="Accommodate-WordPress-Theme" src="http://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Accommodate-WordPress-Theme.jpg" alt="Accommodate-WordPress-Theme" width="525" height="855" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Accommodate-WordPress-Theme</p></div>\n<p>The <a title="Accommodate" href="http://wplook.com/accommodate" target="_blank">Theme</a> looks beautiful at any size, be it a laptop screen, iPad, iPhone, Android Mobile or tablets.</p>\n<p><strong>Theme Features:</strong></p>\n<ul class="list_feature_news">\n<li>Responsive design (Mobile first)</li>\n<li>Custom Post type menu</li>\n<li>Custom Logo</li>\n<li>Custom Background</li>\n<li>Custom CSS</li>\n<li>Custom Widgets</li>\n<li>Share Buttons</li>\n<li>Twitter Integration</li>\n<li>Nivo Slider <em>(a $19 value)</em></li>\n<li>SlidesJS</li>\n<li>Internationalized &amp; localization</li>\n<li>Multiple widget Areas</li>\n<li>Banners widget</li>\n<li>Twitter widget</li>\n<li>Flickr widget</li>\n<li>Drop-down Menu</li>\n<li>WordPress APIs respected</li>\n<li>Clean Code</li>\n<li>Microformats</li>\n<li>Cross-browser compatibility</li>\n<li>Threaded Comments</li>\n<li>Gravatar ready</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/y95k7o4x6Og" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data